                  <p><a href="/big-data/util/download?id=189800882&cat=whitepaper" target="_blank"><img src="http://twimgs.com/informationweek/big_data/reports/research-the-big-data-management-challenge_20886.gif" / alt="Research: The Big Data Management Challenge" title="Research: The Big Data Management Challenge"></a>
                  <div class = "relatedContent2">
                  <div class="relatedItem">
	                  <h3><a href="/big-data/util/download?id=189800882&cat=whitepaper" target="_blank">Research: The Big Data Management Challenge</a></h3>
                       The challenge of big data is real, but most organizations don't differentiate 'big data' from traditional data, and nearly 90% of respondents to our survey use conventional databases as the primary means of handling data. We'll help you understand what constitutes big data (it's not just size) and the numerous management challenges it poses.
                  </div></p>               
                  </div>
